      "parameters": {
        "content": "CP-03-AI-Copywriter\n\nGenerates SEO content with AI, stores the draft in Google Docs, logs metadata, and sends the draft by email.\n\nSteps:\n1. Form Trigger collects topic, keyword, and tone.\n2. Set: Prepare Prompt builds the SEO copywriting prompt.\n3. Basic LLM Chain sends the prompt to OpenAI.\n4. Code: Format Content parses the JSON response and formats the article draft.\n5. Google Docs creates and updates the draft document.\n6. Google Sheets logs topic, tone, document link, and creation time.\n7. Gmail sends the draft link for review.",
